sp.p:
              
              
                That you would not have spied your best advantages,

                for your Majesty in my opinion lay too high, methinks,

                under favour, you should have lain thus.

            
            
              You are welcome from your Country, and this land

              shall show unto you all the kindness that I can make it; 

              what is your name?

            
            I think there is no Lady can affect

            Another Prince, your brother standing by; 

            He doth Eclipse men's virtues so with his.

            
            Not a word; 

            But if thou lovest me, find some subtle way

            To make her understand by signs.

            
            I thank you; 

            My usage here has been the same it was,

            Worthy a royal Conqueror. For my restraint,

            It came unkindly, because much unlooked for; 

            But I must bear it.

            
            If he have beaten him, I grant the case; 

            But how? we cannot be too subtle in this business,

            I say, but how?

            
            Obedience ever makes that noble use of it,

            To which I dedicate my beaten body; 

            I must trouble you a little further, Gentlemen of the Sword.

            
            I must not say so; 

            Nor I must not hear it spoke by the tongue of man.

            You kicked, dear brother! you are merry.

            
            Children and fools are ever credulous,

            And I am both, I think, for I believe; 

            If you dissemble, be it on your head; 

            I will back unto my prison: 
            yet methinks

            I might be kept in some place where you are; 

            For in myself, I find I know not what

            To call it, but it is a great desire

            To see you often.

            
            
              My shame! thou hast less shame than anything; 

              why dost thou keep my Daughter in a prison? why dost

              thou call her Sister, and do this?

            
            
              Bring it out good Father. I will lie, and listen here

              as reverently as to an Angel: if I breath too loud, tell me; 

              for I would be as still as night.
